title: From a Series of Naval Battles for Wedding Festivities of Cosimo Il de'Medici, Jason's Ship
description: An elaborately decorated ship in profile moving from left to right with many banners raised.  Soldiers stand on the deck of the ship as well as Jason, wearing a large helmet and seated towards the left.  A goddess figure sits behind Jason in the rear of the ship holding a spear and shield.
name: Print
